  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of them-- a lot of them were also with our transfer, there a lot of from Lemberg ghetto what they put on our transfer-- engineers, doctors.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They could-- they never know this kind of work to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they didn't know even how to take the-- this-- the stones out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I used to go in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I used to show it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you want to take out the stone, you have to go from the side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Start from the side.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then it'll keep pulling away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When you, when you chip like this, you can't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a lot of the Ukrainian police, he say, why you show him?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, why don't you show him?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he know that I have another job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I get another job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Means when they finished the job, how much is finished every-- you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a special bag, a plastic bag with stones with all kind of materials to put in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If it's too high, pull it out, straighten it out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If it's too low, fill it in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was my job.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they know the meister needed me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They don't have nobody, you know, that know this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I was from a village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to know everything all around, the works.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I keep, I keep telling them, you know, when the hands swollen up, you keep working who is not used to this kind of work especially.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the hands swollen up over here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That didn't give you no, no, no gloves or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it was just who couldn't work, you stay in the, in the, in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You stay in the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you, you get shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
